<node CREATED="1282835995406" FOLDED="true" ID="Freemind_Link_371460682" MODIFIED="1282836079890" TEXT="There are four kinds of dependencies with &#xa;respect to ordering terminal elements: FS, FF, SS, SF ">
<node CREATED="1282836136859" ID="Freemind_Link_1355745050" MODIFIED="1282836140125" TEXT="1. FS: Designing and coding"/>
<node CREATED="1282836149390" ID="Freemind_Link_192181531" MODIFIED="1282836203843" TEXT="2. SF: &apos;A&apos; is working at a shift-based job and must &#xa;have an overlap to give a report to replacement &apos;B&apos;, &#xa;who is held up in a snowstorm. The actual start of &#xa;the B&apos;s shift controls the finish of A&apos;s - a start-to-finish dependency"/>
<node CREATED="1282836214343" ID="Freemind_Link_195082898" MODIFIED="1282836224875" TEXT="3. SS: When building two walls from a novel material, &#xa;one might start the second wall 2 days after the first so &#xa;that the second team can learn from the first"/>
<node CREATED="1282836240812" ID="Freemind_Link_302704800" MODIFIED="1282836266281" TEXT="4. FF: The document for &apos;Activity A&apos; should finish 5 days &#xa;before the document for &apos;Activity B&apos; so that the reviewers &#xa;have time to read each individually. Although &#xa;Document A and Document B may take different &#xa;times to write, they will be planned to finish 5 days apart."/>
</node>
<node CREATED="1282836082484" FOLDED="true" ID="Freemind_Link_1647679771" MODIFIED="1282836092625" TEXT="There are three kinds of dependencies with &#xa;respect to the reason for the existence of dependency&#xa;">
<node CREATED="1282836283546" ID="Freemind_Link_1961454949" MODIFIED="1282836287812" TEXT="1. Causal (logical) &#xa;    a. It is impossible to edit a text before it is written &#xa;    b. It is illogical to pour concrete before you dig the foundations "/>
<node CREATED="1282836294781" ID="Freemind_Link_1693126291" MODIFIED="1282836301328" TEXT="2. Resource Constraints &#xa;    a. It is logically possible to paint four walls in a room &#xa;        simultaneously but there is only one painter "/>
<node CREATED="1282836312375" ID="Freemind_Link_300799191" MODIFIED="1282836316359" TEXT="3. Discretionary (preferential) &#xa;    a. I want to paint the living room before painting the &#xa;        dining room, although I could do it the other way round, too"/>
</node>
</node>
